doc.title: Tikhonjiso letinemagama esizinda lehlukene
doc.excludeDomains: Ngeta emagama esizinda kutsi angafakwa Ligama lesizinda linye kuphela lelingangetwa ngesikhatsi sinye.
doc.description: Lokucushwa kuvuswa uma ligama lesizinda lehlukile.

example.domain: Ungangeta ligama lesizinda, njenge {{url}}, kute ungafaki lonkhe ligama lesizinda.
example.url: Ungakhipha tikhonjiso letitsite ngekwengeta sikhonjiso, njenge {{url}}.
example.glob: Ungangeta iphethini {{glob}}, njenge <khodi>{{kufana lokuncane}}</khodi>, yekuhambisana lokungacacile.
